item.title: CVE-2022-31598|2024-08-03T07:25:59.514Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20business%20objects
item.description: Due to insufficient input validation, SAP Business Objects - version 420, allows an authenticated attacker to submit a malicious request through an allowed operation. On successful exploitation, an attacker can view or modify information causing a limited impact on confidentiality and integrity of the application.
